<section data-label="11 Vier bouwstenen">
  <div class="slide-frame">
    <div class="eyebrow">De vier bouwstenen</div>
    <h2 class="title" style="margin-top: 28px;">Onthoud deze <span class="accent">vier woorden</span>.<br/>Ze komen straks bij elk voorbeeld terug.</h2>

    <div style="margin-top: 64px; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;">
    <div class="bouwsteen-grid">

      <div class="bouwsteen" style="--c: #06b6d4;">
        <div class="bs-head">
          <div class="bs-ico">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="bs-num">01</span>
        </div>
        <h3>LLM</h3>
        <p class="bs-role">De motor.</p>
        <p class="bs-desc">Tekst in, tekst uit. Praten, samenvatten, redeneren. <em>GPT, Claude, Gemini.</em></p>
      </div>

      <div class="bouwsteen" style="--c: #4f6cf7;">
        <div class="bs-head">
          <div class="bs-ico">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M3 5v14a9 3 0 0 0 18 0V5"/><path d="M3 12a9 3 0 0 0 18 0"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="bs-num">02</span>
        </div>
        <h3>RAG</h3>
        <p class="bs-role">De kennis.</p>
        <p class="bs-desc">Jouw documenten doorzoekbaar voor de LLM. Antwoorden mét bron in plaats van verzinsels.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bouwsteen" style="--c: #f59e0b;">
        <div class="bs-head">
          <div class="bs-ico">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="bs-num">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Tools</h3>
        <p class="bs-role">De armen.</p>
        <p class="bs-desc">Niet alleen praten, ook doen. Mail versturen, agenda inplannen, factuur boeken.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bouwsteen dark">
        <div class="bs-head">
          <div class="bs-ico">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v6m0 10v6m11-11h-6M7 12H1m17.36-7.36l-4.24 4.24m-4.24 4.24l-4.24 4.24m12.72 0l-4.24-4.24m-4.24-4.24L4.64 4.64"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="bs-num">04</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Agents</h3>
        <p class="bs-role">De collega.</p>
        <p class="bs-desc">Beslist zelf welke tools, in welke volgorde, om jouw doel te bereiken.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 32px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;">
        <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0891b2" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/></svg>
        <span style="font-size: 24px; color: var(--ink-3);">En bij alles wat volgt: <strong style="color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600;">jij blijft aan het stuur</strong>. De AI stelt voor, jij beslist.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="chrome">
      <div class="sa-brand"><img src="assets/logo.svg" alt="">Smart<span class="accent">Agents</span></div>
      <div>11 / 32</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
